'''Sherzod Innatillo oʻgʻli Nasrullayev''' ([[Cyrillic|Uzbek Cyrillic]]: Шерзод Иннатилло ўғли Насруллаев; born 23 July 1998) is an Uzbek professional footballer who plays as a [[left-back]] for [[FC Nasaf|Nasaf]] and the [[Uzbekistan national football team|Uzbekistan national team]].

==Club career==
Nasrullaev began his senior career with [[FC Nasaf|Nasaf]] in 2018. He helped them win 3 consecutive [[Uzbekistan Cup]]s and 1 [[Uzbekistan Super Cup]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://kun.uz/ru/60244623|title="Насаф" — обладатель Кубка Узбекистана в третий раз подряд|first=Kun|last=uz|website=Kun.uz|access-date=2024-01-03|archive-date=2024-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20240103201500/https://kun.uz/ru/60244623|url-status=live}}</ref>

==International career==
Nasrullaev was called up to the [[Uzbekistan national under-21 football team|Uzbekistan U21]]s to a youth tournament in 2018, and won the prize for "goal of the tournament" for his game-winning goal in the final.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://kun.uz/ru/91676345|title=Футбол: "молодежка" Узбекистана стала победителем турнира в Китае|first=Kun|last=uz|website=Kun.uz|access-date=2024-01-03|archive-date=2024-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20240103201501/https://kun.uz/ru/91676345|url-status=live}}</ref> He was part of the [[Uzbekistan national under-23 football team|Uzbekistan U23]]s at the [[2020 AFC U-23 Championship]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ufa.uz/2019/12/15/ozbekiston-u-23-terma-jamoasi-ertaga-baaga-yol-oladi|title=Ўзбекистон U-23 терма жамоаси эртага БААга йўл олади|website=ufa.uz|access-date=2024-01-03|archive-date=2019-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191216113412/http://www.ufa.uz/2019/12/15/ozbekiston-u-23-terma-jamoasi-ertaga-baaga-yol-oladi|url-status=dead}}</ref>

Nasrullaev was first called up to the senior [[Uzbekistan national football team|Uzbekistan national team]] in 2022.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://kazfootball.kz/news/68459|title=Сборная Казахстана в товарищеском матче всухую уступила Узбекистану|website=kazfootball.kz|access-date=2024-01-03|archive-date=2024-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20240103201500/http://kazfootball.kz/news/68459|url-status=live}}</ref> He was called up to the national team for the [[2023 AFC Asian Cup]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://xabar.uz/g4jx|title=Ўзбекистон терма жамоасининг Осиё Кубогида қатнашадиган таркиби эълон қилинди|website=xabar.uz|access-date=2024-01-03|archive-date=2024-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20240118153445/https://xabar.uz/g4jx|url-status=live}}</ref>

